step-certctl (0.1.5) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: remove IP: prefix support from SAN config — bare IPs are passed
    directly and step-cli auto-detects them by format
  * Docs: update all example configs and README to use bare IP addresses
  * Test: add SAN handling tests (single, multiple, spaces, trailing comma,
    bare IPv4/IPv6); fix version test to not hardcode version number

 -- Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>  Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

step-certctl (0.1.4) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: split SAN config on commas into separate --san flags; previously
    the entire string was passed as one flag causing malformed SANs
  * Fix: trim leading/trailing whitespace from each SAN entry
  * Fix: skip empty SAN entries from trailing commas

 -- Mohamed Reda Elkhadiri <mohamed@elkhadiri.com>  Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

step-certctl (0.1.3) stable; urgency=low

  * Fix: detect when step ca renew skips renewal (expires-in threshold not
    met) and exit cleanly instead of overwriting with empty temp file
  * Fix: make certificate backup non-fatal so pmxcfs (Proxmox) read-only
    filesystem errors don't abort a successful renewal

